facts.fact_text: At constant 2018 prices, net official development assistance (ODA) increased from 14.3 million dollars in 2000 to 73.0 million dollars in 2019.

facts.seriesTitle: Foreign direct investment (FDI) inflows (millions of dollars)
facts.fact_text: Foreign direct investment (FDI) inflows reached -335.8 million dollars in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Remittances in dollars as a proportion of total GDP (percent)
facts.fact_text: In 2018, the inflow of personal remittances was 0.7 % of GDP , down from 1.0 % in 1990

facts.seriesTitle: Fixed Internet broadband subscriptions (per 100 inhabitants)
facts.fact_text: Fixed-broadband internet penetration reached increased from 0.8 per 100 inhabitants in 2000 to 40.6 per 100 inhabitants in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Internet users  (per 100 inhabitants)
facts.fact_text: The number of Internet users per 100 inhabitants increased from 44.5 in 2000 to 99.0 in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Worldwide weighted tariff-average, most-favoured-nation status (percent)
facts.fact_text: The worldwide weighted tariff-average for countries with most-favoured-nation status declined from 2.7 % in 2005 to 1.7% in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Worldwide weighted tariff-average, preferential status (percent)
facts.fact_text: The worldwide weighted tariff-average for countries with preferential status declined from 1.2 % in 2005 to 1.1% in 2018.
